{
  "description": "This image depicts a wide shot of the San Francisco-Oakland Bay Bridge on a cloudy day. A vibrant rainbow arcs across the sky above the bridge, originating and terminating somewhere outside the frame. The bridge itself is a prominent steel structure spanning a choppy gray body of water.  Small boats and a possible ship are visible in the water around the bridge's supports. In the far background, the hazy outlines of the city skyline can be seen. The water has some texture and appears slightly turbulent. The sky is overcast with dark, heavy clouds, creating a dramatic contrast with the rainbow.",
